### **4. 37_RealtimeGraphDisplay**  
**Description:**  
A Python-based real-time chart viewer for incoming numerical data.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealtimeGraphDisplay - Live Chart Visualization Tool

RealtimeGraphDisplay creates animated charts for data streams using Matplotlib.

## Features
- Auto-updating line graph  
- Simulated or live data input  
- Pause/resume visualization  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_RealtimeGraphDisplay.git
cd 37_RealtimeGraphDisplay
python visualize.py
